---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cabins at Lusoi Gardens - Cozy Accommodation Near Mount Kenya"
  activePage="cabins"
  description="Discover five beautifully designed cabins at Lusoi Gardens, each with two ensuite bedrooms, private verandahs, and spectacular views of Mount Kenya. Book your cozy cabin retreat today."
  keywords="Lusoi Gardens cabins, accommodation Mount Kenya, cabins Nyeri, family cabins Kenya, resort cabins, Mount Kenya accommodation, ensuite cabins Kenya"
  ogImage="/images/room-ft6.jpg"
>
  <div class="hero-wrap" style="background-image: url('/images/landing-3.jpg');">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row no-gutters slider-text d-flex align-itemd-end justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-9 ftco-animate text-center d-flex align-items-end justify-content-center">
          <div class="text">
            <p class="breadcrumbs mb-2"><span class="mr-2"><a href="/">Home</a></span> <span>Cabins</span></p>
            <h1 class="mb-4 bread">Our Cabins</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="ftco-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 text-center ftco-animate">
          <span class="subheading">Accommodation</span>
          <h2 class="cabin-main-heading mb-4">Family Nest Cabins</h2>
          <p class="cabin-intro-text">Lusoi Gardens features five beautifully designed cabins, each with two ensuite bedrooms, offering privacy and comfort for every guest. Every cottage has its own private entrance and a verandah that opens to the most spectacular views. Guests can also enjoy a cozy common lounge, complete with a welcoming fireplace where family and friends gather to bond over stories and a hot cup of cocoa.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature image -->
  <section class="ftco-no-pt ftco-no-pb">
    <div class="container-fluid px-0">
      <div class="cabin-hero-img" style="background-image: url(/images/exterior-3.jpg);"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bedroom - Image Right -->
  <section class="ftco-section ftco-no-pb">
    <div class="container-fluid px-0">
      <div class="row no-gutters align-items-stretch">
        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center ftco-animate">
          <div class="cabin-detail-text">
            <h3>Bedroom</h3>
            <p>The room features a polished wooden floor that adds warmth and character, complemented by a handcrafted wooden bed that anchors the space with rustic charm. A reading light by the bedside creates a cozy nook for evening reflection or quiet study. With its spacious layout, the room invites relaxation and ease, offering guests both comfort and a sense of openness.</p>
            <p>Notable amenities include:</p>
            <ul class="cabin-features">
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> 2 Queen sized double beds</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Complimentary drinking water</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> 4 Plush pillows per bed</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Open wardrobe</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Extra warm blanket</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Full length mirror</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Solar heated shower</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 ftco-animate">
          <div class="cabin-detail-img" style="background-image: url(/images/room-ft2.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Lounge - Image Left -->
  <section class="ftco-section ftco-no-pb">
    <div class="container-fluid px-0">
      <div class="row no-gutters align-items-stretch">
        <div class="col-md-6 ftco-animate">
          <div class="cabin-detail-img" style="background-image: url(/images/lounge.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center ftco-animate">
          <div class="cabin-detail-text">
            <h3>Lounge</h3>
            <p>The lounge is a warm and inviting space designed for both relaxation and connection. At its heart stands a charming fireplace, casting a gentle glow that creates a cozy atmosphere for gatherings or quiet reflection.  The lounge can comfortably serve as a workstation for business travellers thanks to the complimentary wifi that is available in all cabins.</p>
            {/* <ul class="cabin-features">
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Kitchenette</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Microwave</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Mini fridge</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Private entrance</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Verandah with views</li>
            </ul> */}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Essentials - Image Right -->
  <section class="ftco-section">
    <div class="container-fluid px-0">
      <div class="row no-gutters align-items-stretch">
        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center ftco-animate">
          <div class="cabin-detail-text">
            <h3>Kitchenette</h3>
            <p>Just steps away from the lounge, a spacious kitchenette offers convenience and functionality, making it easy to prepare light meals or refreshments.</p>
            <p>Notable amenities include:</p>
            <ul class="cabin-features">
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Mini fridge</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Electric cooker</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Microwave</li>
              <li><span class="icon-check"></span> Ample storage space</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 ftco-animate">
          <div class="cabin-detail-img" style="background-image: url(/images/kitchenette.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gallery strip -->
  <section class="ftco-no-pt ftco-no-pb">
    <div class="container-fluid px-0">
      <div class="row no-gutters">
        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="cabin-thumb" style="background-image: url(/images/room-featured.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="cabin-thumb" style="background-image: url(/images/room-ft3.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="cabin-thumb" style="background-image: url(/images/room-ft5.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
          <div class="cabin-thumb" style="background-image: url(/images/room-ft7.jpg);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ftco-section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 text-center ftco-animate">
          <h2 class="cabin-main-heading mb-4">Ready to Experience Lusoi Gardens?</h2>
          <p class="cabin-intro-text mb-4">Perfect for both intimate stays and group getaways, our cabins blend rustic charm with modern convenience, making every visit a memorable retreat.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-5">Book Your Stay</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .cabin-main-heading {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: #000;
  }

  .cabin-intro-text {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* Hero image */
  .cabin-hero-img {
    height: 550px;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  /* Alternating detail blocks */
  .cabin-detail-img {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    min-height: 500px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .cabin-detail-text {
    padding: 4em 5em;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .cabin-detail-text h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .cabin-detail-text h3::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 50px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: #b69100;
  }

  .cabin-detail-text p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  /* Feature list */
  .cabin-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cabin-features li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: #555;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .cabin-features li .icon-check {
    color: #b69100;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  /* Gallery strip */
  .cabin-thumb {
    height: 250px;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767.98px) {
    .cabin-hero-img {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .cabin-detail-img {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .cabin-detail-text {
      padding: 3em 2em;
    }

    .cabin-detail-text h3 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .cabin-thumb {
      height: 180px;
    }
  }
</style>
